Wide Range for Outdoor LED Displays

Outdoor LED Displays are ideal for outdoor rental, staging and flexible-fixed applications. Each lightweight display is suitable for hanging and free-standing installations. It is designed to perform in outdoor environments. Earning an IP65 Protection Rating, the dust-tight enclosure of the displays works to protect the LED display in outdoor installations.
People are on the move and spending most of their time out of home in multiple places: on the street, in corporate buildings, shopping malls, retail stores or transportation hubs. To reach these mobile audiences with advertising or information is an ever challenging task, which requires impactful and targeted message delivery.Outdoor LED screens are large, bright and made for impact. Being digital, they allow for targeted message delivery at the right location and right place, for reaching mobile consumers during their weekly routines.

Key Features

  • Curving Capabilities
  • Seamless and adaptable to nearly any size or shape
  • Designed to limit power consumption
  • Slim Design & Light weight cabinet
  • Innovative and Flexible LED Signage Solution
  • Automatic Calibration function
  • High refresh rate.
  • Intelligent Front Access

Outdoor LED Displays

Ultra Series

SMD Series
SMD Series LED Display supports auto reload data technology and the calibration data is stored in module.
Fixed Series
Fixed Series featured with a 45 degree bevel in which internal & outer arc spliced smoothly.
